french inflat slow in februari french inflat slow in februari to between 0.1 and 0.2 pct against 0.9 pct in januari , the nation statist institut ( inse ) said . the retail price index show a year-on-year rise of 3.4 pct against three pct in januari . an inse offici said the final figur for februari would be releas later thi month . after januari 's rise the govern wa forc to revis it inflat target for 1987 to 2.5 pct year on year from an initi target of two pct , after 2.1 pct in 1986. financ minist edouard balladur said half the januari rise wa due to higher oil price and forecast a februari slow .